    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ActionTaken
    Represents an action taken within a Jeopardy turn
    AnswerQuestionAction
    represents an AnswerQuestionAction object within a Jeopardy turn
    CSVReader
    Creates a CSVReader object capable of reading questions from a CSV file
    CSVReportGenerator
    Generates a CSV report from the game log
    DOCXReportGenerator
    Generates a DOCX report from the game log
    Game
    Represents an instance of the game of Jeopardy
    GameEvent
    Represents an event that occurs during the game, capturing relevant details for logging purposes
    GameLogger
    Logs game events and generates reports in various formats
    GameObserver
    Represents an observer within the game of Jeopardy
    JeopardySession
     
    JSONReader
    Creates a JSONReader object capable of reading questions from a JSON file
    PDFReportGenerator
    Generates a PDF report from the game log
    Player
    Represents a player within the game of Jeopardy
    Question
    Represents a question in the game with its category, value, text, options, and correct answer
    Reader
    Represents a reader capable of reading questions from a data source
    ReportGenerator
    Interface for generating reports from game logs
    SelectQuestionAction
    Represents the action of a question being selected in the game of Jeopardy
    TXTReportGenerator
    Generates a TXT report from the game log
    Vault
    Represents a vault that stores and manages a collection of questions for the game
    XMLReader
    Creates an XMLReader object capable of reading questions from an XML file
